<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[١١١٠٥]</span> مِرْدَاسُ بْنُ مَافَنَّه، <span class="c4">[أبو]</span> عُبَيْدَةَ <span class="c2">(١)</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span> <span class="c2">(٣)</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">نَا أَبُو رُفَيْقٍ قَالَ:</span> سَأَلْتُ وَهْبَ بْنَ مُنبِّهٍ عَنِ الدَّنَانِيرِ وَالدَّرَاهِمِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
